related_questions.question: Was there a sequel to Batman Begins?
related_questions.snippet: The Dark Knight is a 2008 superhero film directed by Christopher Nolan from a screenplay co-written with his brother Jonathan. Based on the DC Comics superhero Batman, it is the sequel to Batman Begins (2005) and the second installment in The Dark Knight Trilogy.

related_questions.question: Are any of the Batman movies connected?
related_questions.snippet: That's because while there have been many different takes on Batman to hit the big screen, only a few are connected at any given time. You could watch all of the Batman movies from the '90s and completely ignore everything else if you wanted to. You could do the same with Christopher Nolan's trilogy.
